# 11 - API Builder
# Generate a REST API from a spec

NAME api-builder
INPUT spec_file
INPUT language DEFAULT "go"
INPUT framework DEFAULT "gin"

GOAL parse_spec "Read $spec_file. List endpoints and schemas concisely."
GOAL design "Design minimal $language/$framework structure: handlers + routes. Skip middleware unless specified."
GOAL generate "Generate API code. Basic error handling. Brief comments only."
GOAL write_files "Write files to appropriate locations."

RUN build USING parse_spec, design, generate, write_files
